{"version": "https://jsonfeed.org/version/1.1", "title": "Notes", "home_page_url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/", "feed_url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/feed_json_updated.json", "description": "Learning notes.", "icon": null, "authors": [{"name": "ShenMian"}], "language": "zh", "items": [{"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F/Broken_Arrow/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F/Broken_Arrow/", "title": "Broken Arrow", "content_html": "<h1>Broken Arrow</h1>\n<p><strong>\u4e2d\u6587</strong>: \u65ad\u7bad.  </p>\n<h2>\u5361\u7ec4</h2>\n<p>\u5361\u7ec4\u6587\u4ef6\u4f4d\u4e8e <code>%USERPROFILE%\\AppData\\LocalLow\\SteelBalalaikaStudio\\BrokenArrow\\Decks</code>.</p>\n<h2>\u9632\u7a7a\u538b\u5236</h2>\n<p>\u9632\u7a7a\u538b\u5236 (Suppression of Enemy Ai...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-25T22:54:03+08:00", "date_published": "2026-04-20T15:34:48+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/LLM_%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/LLM_%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/", "title": "LLM \u5165\u95e8\u6307\u5357", "content_html": "<h1>LLM \u5165\u95e8\u6307\u5357</h1>\n<p>\u5927\u8bed\u8a00\u6a21\u578b (Large Language Model, LLM) \u6307\u7531\u5177\u6709\u5927\u91cf\u53c2\u6570 (\u901a\u5e38\u5927\u4e8e 1B) \u7684\u795e\u7ecf\u7f51\u7edc\u7ec4\u6210\u7684\u8bed\u8a00\u6a21\u578b.<br>\n\u672c\u6587\u4e0d\u6d89\u53ca\u6280\u672f\u7ec6\u8282, \u4e13\u95e8\u4ecb\u7ecd<strong>\u5982\u4f55\u4f7f\u7528 LLM</strong>, \u5e2e\u52a9\u8bfb\u8005\u5feb\u901f\u4e0a\u624b.</p>\n<h2>\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef</h2>\n<h3>\u4f18\u70b9</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>\u754c\u9762\u7edf\u4e00</strong>: \u53ef\u4ee5\u901a\u8fc7\u7edf\u4e00\u7684\u754c...</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T14:46:04+08:00", "date_published": "2026-05-21T14:46:04+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/", "title": "Notes", "content_html": "<h1>Notes</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://shenmian.github.io/notes/feed_rss_created.xml\"><img alt=\"RSS - \u65b0\u5efa\u6587\u7ae0\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/RSS-\u65b0\u5efa\u6587\u7ae0-orange?logo=rss&amp;logoColor=white\"></a>\n[![RSS...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T14:39:07+08:00", "date_published": "2026-04-20T15:34:48+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/%E5%A7%BF%E6%80%81%E8%A7%A3%E7%AE%97/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96/%E5%A7%BF%E6%80%81%E8%A7%A3%E7%AE%97/", "title": "\u59ff\u6001\u89e3\u7b97", "content_html": "<h1>\u59ff\u6001\u89e3\u7b97</h1>\n<p><strong>\u5173\u952e\u5b57</strong>: IMU \u6570\u636e\u878d\u5408.</p>\n<p>\u59ff\u6001\u89e3\u7b97\u662f\u6307\u6839\u636e\u52a0\u901f\u5ea6\u8ba1/\u9640\u87ba\u4eea/\u78c1\u529b\u8ba1\u7b49\u7684\u6570\u636e\u878d\u5408\u5728\u4e00\u8d77, \u5f97\u51fa\u98de\u884c\u5668\u7684\u7a7a\u4e2d\u59ff\u6001.</p>\n<p>$$\n\u52a0\u901f\u5ea6\u8ba1 \\rightarrow \u52a0\u901f\u5ea6 \\xrightarrow{\u79ef\u5206} \u901f\u5ea6 \\xrightarrow{\u79ef\u5206} \u4f4d\u7f6e \\ \u9640\u87ba\u4eea \\rightarrow \u89d2\u901f...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T13:38:33+08:00", "date_published": "2026-04-20T15:34:48+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F/FPS_%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F/FPS_%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/", "title": "FPS \u5165\u95e8\u6307\u5357", "content_html": "<h1>FPS \u5165\u95e8\u6307\u5357</h1>\n<p>\u8fd9\u662f\u4e00\u7bc7\u5173\u4e8e\u7b2c\u4e00\u4eba\u79f0\u5c04\u51fb (First-Person Shooter, FPS) \u6e38\u620f\u7684\u901a\u7528\u5165\u95e8\u6307\u5357.  </p>\n<h2>\u4eab\u53d7</h2>\n<p>\u5728\u591a\u4eba\u6e38\u620f\u4e2d, \u4eab\u53d7\u6e38\u620f\u7684\u8fc7\u7a0b\u662f\u6700\u91cd\u8981\u7684\u4e00\u70b9, \u4f46\u4e5f\u662f\u6700\u5bb9\u6613\u88ab\u5ffd\u7565\u7684.<br>\n\u73a9\u5bb6\u5728\u6e38\u620f\u4e2d\u9047\u5230\u5176\u4ed6\u4eba\u7684\u653b\u51fb\u6216\u4f5c\u5f0a\u884c\u4e3a\u65f6, \u5e94\u8be5\u4fdd\u6301\u51b7\u9759, \u4e0d\u8981\u5fd8\u8bb0\u6e38\u620f\u7684\u521d\u8877.<br>\n\u5bf9\u4e8e...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T13:37:57+08:00", "date_published": "2026-04-20T15:34:48+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/Python/Python_%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80/Python/Python_%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4/", "title": "Python \u6545\u969c\u6392\u9664", "content_html": "<h1>Python \u6545\u969c\u6392\u9664</h1>\n<h2>\u5b89\u88c5 pip</h2>\n<p>ModuleNotFoundError: No module named 'pip'</p>\n<p><code>sh\ncurl https://bootstrap.pypa.io/get-pip.py -o get-pip.py\npython get-pip.py</code></p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "date_published": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/Git/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/Git/", "title": "Git", "content_html": "<h1>Git</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"Git \u5e38\u7528\u547d\u4ee4\u901f\u67e5\u8868 - riku.wowubuntu.com\" src=\"assets/git_cheat_sheet.webp\">  </p>\n<p><a href=\"https://git-scm.com/\">Git</a> \u662f\u4e00\u6b3e\u5f00\u6e90 (GPLv2) \u7684\u7248\u672c\u63a7\u5236\u7cfb\u7edf (Version Control System, VCS). \u540d...</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "date_published": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/IRC/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/IRC/", "title": "IRC", "content_html": "<h1>IRC</h1>\n<p>IRC (Internet Relay Chat) \u662f\u4e00\u79cd\u5e94\u7528\u5c42\u7684\u5b9e\u65f6\u804a\u5929\u534f\u8bae.</p>\n<h2>\u5ba2\u6237\u7aef</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Weechat</p>\n<p>Weechat \u662f\u7ec8\u7aef\u4e0b\u7684 IRC \u5ba2\u6237\u7aef, \u914d\u7f6e/\u4f7f\u7528\u8d77\u6765\u5341\u5206\u65b9\u4fbf.<br>\n\u521d\u6b21\u4f7f\u7528 Weechat \u53ef\u4ee5\u53c2\u8003 [Weechat Quick Start Guid...</p>\n</li>\n</ul>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "date_published": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/LibreOffice_%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/LibreOffice_%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4/", "title": "LibreOffice \u6545\u969c\u6392\u9664", "content_html": "<h1>LibreOffice \u6545\u969c\u6392\u9664</h1>\n<h2>\u56fe\u6807\u6a21\u7cca</h2>\n<p>\u5728 <code>Tools | Options... | LibreOffice | View</code> \u4e2d, \u5c06 <code>Icon Theme</code> \u8bbe\u7f6e\u4e3a\u652f\u6301 SVG \u7684\u4e3b\u9898.</p>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "date_published": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "authors": [], "tags": null}, {"id": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/MPV/", "url": "https://shenmian.github.io/notes/%E8%BD%AF%E4%BB%B6%E4%B8%8E%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7/MPV/", "title": "MPV", "content_html": "<h1>MPV</h1>\n<p><img alt=\"MPV \u622a\u56fe\" src=\"assets/mpv.webp\"></p>\n<h2>\u8d85\u5206\u8fa8\u7387 (Super Resolution)</h2>\n<p><code>conf title=\"~~/mpv.conf\"\nvf=d3d11vpp=w=0:h=0:scaling-mode=nvidia</code></p>\n<h2>\u8865\u5e27 (Frame Interpol...</h2>", "image": null, "date_modified": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08:00", "date_published": "2026-05-21T13:13:31+08: